THIS MOD IS FOR RICH PLAYERS. Adds a home to Wolfskull cave, it costs approximately 500k and an extra 100k or so for the room keys. the keys are all craftable from the skyforge. there is now a study, a greenhouse, a wardrobe, a safe, a trophy areaÂ and a kitchen the kitchen will be worked on more in later updates. there is now aetherium armor which only the rich and powerful can obtain. aetherium armor increases your chances of survival considerably when facing skyrims challenges on legendary mode. hearth fire is required, if you whish to gain income faster I recommend [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37774/]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37774/[/url]?
